title: Ep7 Gossip at the Corpse Cart
description: This month, the gals dig into some serious recent injustices plus an all-too-gaseous intruder who might just regret that last burrito. Topics include a fatal white savior complex, yet more dangers of cruise ships, and a majorly maligned manslaughter charge. Tune in for the July episode of Gossip at the Corpse Cart!
